<figureCitation id="B1812DC6FFBECB0CA7CB28BEFEDAFDD7" box="[159,258,490,515]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 7" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1948,1971]" captionTargetBox="[223,1373,200,1911]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[210,1374,193,1921]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 7. Hemerodromia brevicercata sp. nov., 1 – 2, holotype ♂. 3 – 7, paratype ♂. 1, habitus, lateral view; 2, wing; 3, terminalia, lateral view; 4, subepandrial sclerite and epandrium, dorsal view; 5, terminalia, ventral view; 6, phallus, lateral view; 7, apex of the phallus and apex of epandrium, dorsal view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/233673/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="198">
