°), distal to position of M 
<number id="9F722364FFBECB0CA43A2DA4FCABFB2A" box="[878,883,1264,1278]" pageId="1" pageNumber="198" value="1.0">1</number>
+ 
<number id="9F722364FFBECB0CA42A2DA4FC5FFB2A" box="[894,903,1264,1278]" pageId="1" pageNumber="198" value="2.0">2</number>
